      "id": "gap-goals-mission-ref-invalid",
      "description": "Currently dispatched goals (16 goals, mixed priorities) all contain mission_ref placeholders like 'MSP §critical-priority', 'MSP §high-priority', etc. The MSP contains no such sections. Goals are not derived from any substantive mission statement and may be defaults or test artifacts.",
